==Speaking to the costumed children==
* '''Player:''' Hello there!
* '''Costumed child:''' Hi!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What's that giant cauldron doing here?}}
** '''Player:''' What's that giant cauldron doing here?
** '''Costumed child (jack lantern):''' It's collecting treats and looking spooky while doing it!
** '''Player:''' What happens when it's full?
** '''Costumed child (cave horror):''' We don't know, but we're hoping to find out!
** '''Costumed child (spooky outfit):''' Sometimes bats come out of it.
** '''Costumed child (jack lantern):''' Maybe a whole swarm will fly out when it's full!
** '''Costumed child (spooky outfit):'''I hope not!
** '''Player:''' Can anyone put treats in it?
** '''Costumed child (cave horror):''' Of course! It's massive, so we'll need as much help as we can get!
** '''Player:''' I'll do what I can!
** '''Player:''' Do you know how the cauldron got here?
** '''Costumed child (jack lantern):''' We're not sure...
** '''Costumed child (cave horror):''' It was here when we came out to Trick-or-Treat.
** '''Player:''' So you didn't see anyone put it here?
